3:03:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-09-08/ty-article/.premium/u-s-finalizing-new-israel-hamas-cease-fire-proposal-despite-skepticism/00000191-ce14-dd1c-a19b-cf35a77b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列政府的世界末日愿景：将加沙变成约旦河西岸，将约旦河西岸变成加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article/.premium/israels-new-task-the-gazafication-of-the-west-bank/00000191-ce12-d214-a393-cfba5b7c0000</link><description>忘掉在本格维尔的诽谤吧：以色列正面临真正陷入泥潭的风险，因为它着眼于对加沙的军事统治，而约旦河西岸的局势正在各个层面升级</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 03:02:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article/.premium/israels-new-task-the-gazafication-of-the-west-bank/00000191-ce12-d214-a393-cfba5b7c0000</guid></item><item><title>来自约旦的恐怖分子在过境点开枪，三名以色列人丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article-live/reports-three-rescuers-killed-in-israeli-attack-in-lebanon-drone-sirens-in-north-israel/00000191-cf4f-d25e-a1f7-cfcff8cb0000</link><description>以色列国防军：夜间从黎巴嫩向以色列发射了约 50 枚火箭弹；无人员伤亡 ■ 约旦表示正在调查与以色列边境发生的致命枪击事件，关闭过境点直至另行通知 ■ 加沙消息来源报道，加沙北部救援部门副指挥官在贾巴利亚家中遇袭身亡</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 01:54:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article-live/reports-three-rescuers-killed-in-israeli-attack-in-lebanon-drone-sirens-in-north-israel/00000191-cf4f-d25e-a1f7-cfcff8cb0000</guid></item><item><title>法院命令释放涉嫌向本格维尔扔沙子的女子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article/.premium/woman-suspected-of-throwing-sand-at-ben-gvir-released-by-court-order/00000191-ce49-d25e-a1f7-cfcb46e60000</link><description>特拉维夫治安法院法官在观看该事件的短视频后中断听证会，随后将嫌疑人软禁，整个法庭都在抗议对她的拘留。</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Sep 2024 21:50:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article/.premium/woman-suspected-of-throwing-sand-at-ben-gvir-released-by-court-order/00000191-ce49-d25e-a1f7-cfcb46e60000</guid></item><item><title>随着数字影子战争的加剧，以色列军队高层成为错误信息的焦点</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-09-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/as-digital-shadow-war-intensifies-israeli-army-brass-is-in-misinformation-crosshairs/00000191-ccaf-d214-a393-cdbfa9210000</link><description>亲巴勒斯坦的账户发起了一场心理战运动，为巴勒斯坦人提供了短暂的胜利形象，声称以色列国防军高级军官死亡。研究人员将这些错误信息活动追溯到俄罗斯</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Sep 2024 17:44:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-09-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/as-digital-shadow-war-intensifies-israeli-army-brass-is-in-misinformation-crosshairs/00000191-ccaf-d214-a393-cdbfa9210000</guid></item><item><title>以色列处于战争状态，第 337 天：中央情报局局长表示停火协议“最终是一个政治意愿问题”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-07/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-337-cia-chief-says-cease-fire-deal-is-a-question-of-political-will/00000191-cd4e-d214-a393-cdfe57c90000</link><description>纽约时报：哈马斯对人质/停火协议提出了新要求 ■ 加沙医务人员：以色列国防军的袭击在 48 小时内造成至少 61 人死亡 ■ 巴勒斯坦卫生部：以色列国防军在约旦河西岸中部开火，造成 13 岁女孩死亡 ■ 英国军情六处负责人: 伊朗仍计划对哈马斯领导人哈尼亚被杀事件进行报复 ■ 战争已过去 337 天，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Sep 2024 17:20:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-07/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-337-cia-chief-says-cease-fire-deal-is-a-question-of-political-will/00000191-cd4e-d214-a393-cdfe57c90000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡“在他的联盟的祭坛上牺牲了我的兄弟”：以色列人抗议人质释放协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-07/ty-article/.premium/a-week-of-protests-israelis-take-to-the-streets-to-demand-netanyahu-make-a-hostage-deal/00000191-cd22-deaf-a1f1-cdb7ed5e0000</link><description>在从加沙地带打捞出六名人质尸体后，本周每晚都会发生抗议活动。一名人质的母亲说：“只要内塔尼亚胡掌权，我们就会继续把人质装进裹尸袋”</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Sep 2024 16:21:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-07/ty-article/.premium/a-week-of-protests-israelis-take-to-the-streets-to-demand-netanyahu-make-a-hostage-deal/00000191-cd22-deaf-a1f1-cdb7ed5e0000</guid></item><item><title>《国土报》摄影师拍摄的以色列一周</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israels-week-in-pictures-by-haaretz-photographers/00000191-cccc-deaf-a1f1-cdff7af80000</link><description></description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Sep 2024 15:34:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israels-week-in-pictures-by-haaretz-photographers/00000191-cccc-deaf-a1f1-cdff7af80000</guid></item></channel></rss>